體等傳播工具，\r\n    對公眾散布而犯之。","JFULLPDF":"https://data.judicial.gov.tw/jdg/api/JDocFile/TCDM/111%2c%e9%87%91%e8%a8%b4%2c1007%2c20220815%2c1/pdf"},"JID":"TCDM,111,金訴,1007,20220815,1","JYEAR":"111","JCASE":"金訴","JNO":"1007","JDATE":"20220815","JTITLE":"詐欺等"}